{
  "text": "Wilky et al. [CITATION_1] carried out a phase ii trial of axitinibpembrolizumab in patients with advanced alveolar softpart sarcoma (asps) and other sts subtypes that enrolled 33 patients. At a median follow-up of 14.7 months, the 6-month progression-free survival (pfs) was 47% (95% confidence interval: 29.2% to 62.8%), and the 12-month pfs was 28%.",
